_sText:
DESCRIPTION:  de_rotterdam_css is a re-made version of the de_rotterdam map for the original Counter-strike.  de_rotterdam_css is a bomb defusal map that takes place at dusk.

* I made this map a while ago... but I just recently came back to this map, fixed it up, added a few cool things to it, and made sure the T's did not have such a disadvantage! *
____________

Please inform me before redistributing on CD, DVD etc.  NOT to be sold, modified or "plugged" into a mod without notifying me.

Have fun and enjoy!

-=Worm Maps=-
____________

*note*
Some of the custom textures throughout the map have been taken from sites. (credit to those who took/made those pics).
